OAKLAND, Ca. -- Masu zanga-zanga a California sun bude wuta a gaban kotu, sun lalata ofishin 'yan sanda da kuma cin zarafin jami'ai bayan da zanga-zangar lumana ta tsananta a yammacin Asabar, inji 'yan sandan Oakland.
Masu zanga-zanga sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa fentin zane-zane, sun harbe wuta da kuma nuna Lasers a jami’an, sashen Oakland ya ce a Twitter .
Kafofin watsa labarai da dama sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shiryawa da su " taimaka mana mu samar da wurare masu hadari da kuma wuraren da za su iya zama masu zanga-zanga."
An fara zanga-zangar ne a farkon ranar Asabar da yamma tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms," kama daga wata kungiyar da ta kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan birnin don tsare wani gidan gwamnatin tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya aike da jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don matsa lamba a kan zanga-zangar da ta auku cikin dare tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi a Oakland ta fara lumana, amma ta juya baya cikin dare.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ayyana wani taron "unlawful assembly" da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare kuma jami'ai sun nemi jama'a su tarwatsa.
Wutar ta tashi ne a unguwar Alameda County Superior Court kuma tana dauke ne da dan kankanin lokaci daga baya, kamfanin dillancin labarai ya ruwaito.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zanga a wani lokaci "sun yi taho mu gama da tagogi da kuma rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata a mazauna wurin."
