SAATTLE - Bayan makonni da arangama tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., jama'a kimanin 2,000 suka yi gangami a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna yin zanga-zanga a kan tituna da kuma yin arangama da 'yan sanda.
An raunata jami'an 'yan sanda uku, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti tare da raunin kafa sakamakon fashewar, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 tun da yamma, in ji 'yan sanda.
Masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da ake tsare da matasa a nan gaba kuma suka kona gine-gine a can kan wuta.
Wasu sun fasa tagogi na kasuwancin da ke kusa.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci taron jama'a a unguwar Capitol Hill, suna amfani da gurneti na flash da kuma barkono kafin su fara daukar mutane a tsare.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, na Kirkland, Wash., ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun a watan Mayu kuma ta ce abin takaici ne a gare ta ta ga irin wannan dabaru da 'yan sanda suka yi.
"Wannan ba kasar da na yi hijira ba ce", in ji Ms. Mukherjee, wadda ta zo daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka wuce.
"Yana jin kamar muna saurin zama jihar masu fafutika da kuma jihar 'yan sanda."
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce an yi zanga-zangar ne da nufin duka kananan hukumomi da kuma tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da suka yi zanga-zangar da aka dade ana yi a Portland.
Mr. Savage ya ce dabarar da ake da ita a Portland, wadda ta hada da amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye da kuma munin taro, ta kasance mai haɗari kuma bai dace ba.
"Yana da matukar wuyar nunewa a cikin wani mummunan shugabanci," Mr. Savage ya ce yayin da ya wanke idanunsa na barkono kuma ya yi jinyar rauni a kan hannu daga gurneti.
