Sakatare Janar na gida Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram kan sakonnin Wiley
Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a tsawon lokacin da ya dauki don cire "abhorrent" posts da Wiley ya yi.
A halin yanzu 'yan sanda suna gudanar da bincike a kan jerin kalaman da aka wallafa kan asusun yanar gizo na Grime.
Sakataren Gida ya fada a ranar Lahadi cewa: "Abubuwa masu karya garkuwar jiki daga Wiley suna da ban tsoro."
"Ya kamata ba su iya kasancewa a Twitter da Instagram tsawon lokaci ba kuma na nemi cikakken bayani."
"Kamfanin kafofin watsa labarun dole ne su yi saurin kawar da irin wannan kiyayya daga cikin dandamali."
An zargi Twitter da "mutumin karya" yayin da har yanzu Wiley tweets suna bayyane sa'o'i 12 bayan an fara wallafa su.
Tun da farko an cire tweets da dama kuma an fitar da 41-year-old a cikin kwana bakwai da shafin.
Twitter a baya ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na ɗan lokaci "don karya manufofinmu na ƙiyayya," yayin da Facebook ya ce "babu wani wuri don kalaman kiyayya a kan Instagram."
Hukumar 'yan sandan ta ce a ranar Asabar: "Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta dauki duk wasu rahotanni na antisemitism da muhimmanci sosai.
A halin da ake ciki, kamfanin gudanarwa na Wiley, A-List Management, "cut all ties" da tauraron.
Tsohon manajan mai zane a yanzu, John Woolf, wanda Yahudawa ne, ya rubuta a Twitter cewa: "Bi da kalaman Wiley na antisemitic a yau mu a @A_ListMGMT sun yanke duk dangantaka da shi. Babu wani wuri a cikin al'umma don antisemitism."
A baya ya ce ba ya goyon baya ko kuma ya yi ta’aziyya ga abin da Wiley ya wallafa amma zai yi magana da shi a kansa kuma ya " taimaka wajen ilmantar da shi."
Duk da haka, a wani bidiyo a Instagram, Wiley ya bayyana cewa shi ne wanda ya yanke dangantaka da gudanarwarsa.
Sauran 'yan majalisa sun caccaki Twitter saboda ƙyale tweets su kasance a bayyane.
Dan majalisar Labour Jess Phillips ya ce a ranar Asabar:
"Ka ga dukan Wiley stuff. Me ya sa a duniya sun @Twitter bar up irin mugun antisemitism da ƙiyayya? Yana hits dukan m beats, Yahudawa samun abubuwa ba ka samu, su ne a iko, suna zaton su mafi alh<unk>ri... Wannan shi ne m stuff. Tabbas ya kamata ya sauko."
Fellow MP Neil Coyle ya kara da cewa: "His management appear able to act quicker than @Twitter emphasising, once again, cewa dokokin (ciki har da Online Harms Bill) ya kamata tabbatar da kafofin watsa labarun dandamali ba a amfani da su don yada ƙiyayya."
John Mann, mai ba da shawara na gwamnati mai zaman kanta game da antisemitism, ya ce kalaman "za su nuna ainihin dalilin da ya sa dokar na bukatar canzawa don rike su zuwa asusun da ya dace."
A halin da ake ciki kuma, Kungiyar Yaki da Cin Hanci da Rashawa ta nemi 'yan sanda su binciki abun da Wiley ke ciki, sannan ta yi kira ga a rufe asusunsa na kafofin watsa labarun "don hana kara fitar da zafin kishin Yahudawa."
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather of Grime kuma sunansa na ainihi Richard Cowie, ya sami lambar MBE don ayyukan waƙa a 2018.
