Magajin garin Kansas ya yi maraba da taimakon tarayya wajen warware kisan kai, amma ya damu da muradin Trump
Magajin garin Kansas Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi game da muradin Shugaba Trump na tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen warware wani hanzari na kisan gilla a tsakiyar birnin, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama karin game da bugu da karimcin sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi takaici sosai a wannan makon [da] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci ƙungiyoyin Black Lives Matter," Lucas, dan Democrat, ya ce a kan "Fox News Sunday" na zanga-zangar baya-bayan nan kan rashin daidaiton launin fata da kuma zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka ba ne a Kansas City. Mun yi ƙaruwa na shekara-shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kan shi ne a zahiri share wasu daga cikin kisan da ba a warware su ba."
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Let's try to have a pinpointed and targeted focus on solving murders...I think if you listen to recent statements... we are happy to work with federal agents in a limited scope."
Duk da cewa ya yarda da jami'an gwamnatin tarayya su yi aiki tare da hukumomin shari'a na yankin, Lucas ya ce, kalaman Trump - musamman ma a game da takaddamar da ke tattare da dabarun da ake amfani da su a Portland, Ore., ta hanyar jami'an gwamnatin tarayya - ya sa mutane da yawa daga cikin 'yan majalisarsa su nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a kan titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukata ba shi ne karin man fetur a kan wuta daga jami'an tarayya don yin, ina ganin, wani lamari mai ban sha'awa na siyasa," in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa, ya tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen magance tashin wasu laifuka - matakin da ke nuni da fadada matakin shiga fadar White House cikin dokokin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da bayyana kansa a matsayin shugaban "yan sanda da oda".
Jami'an "surge" da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da wasu biranen Amurka suna cikin Operation Legend - mai suna bayan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka yi fatali da shi yayin da yake barci a wani gida na Kansas City a yammacin watan jiya.
Duk da yake aika jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don taimakawa wajen gudanar da harkokin shari'a na gida ba abin da ya faru ba - Atoni Janar Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkuri a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin na tarayya da ake aikawa, da kuma wasu dabarunsu, sun tayar da damuwa tsakanin jihohi da 'yan majalisar dokokin yankin.
Wasu 'yan majalisar dokoki daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana kan gwamnatin Trump ta tura jami'anta zuwa garuruwansu, musamman biyo bayan rahotannin da ke cewa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun dauke su a cikin motocin da ba a san su ba.
Portland an buga tare da kusan kullum zanga-zanga kan 'yan sanda da kuma nuna wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da ake tsare da 'yan sandan Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
