Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwa da kafafen yada labarai ta hanyar yin tazarce a siyasa maimakon bayani - da alama ya manta cewa manema labarai sun zabi tambayoyin.
Wata talifin Asabar da AP, babban kamfanin dillancin labarai na Amurka, ya ce labaran fadar White House na iya zama "al'ada mai karya garkuwar jiki," kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "a tallace-tallace mai cike da tallace-tallace ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zabensa, wurin kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da aka gwada haske kan bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
A ƙarshen waɗannan maganganun ba su da masaniya, kamar yadda babu wani sabon bayani da za a bayyana a cikin bayanan.
Abin da AP ya kasa ambata shi ne, da wuya a zahiri an nemi wani sabon bayani a wajen zantawa.
Masu ba da rahoto akai-akai suna amfani da maneman fadar White House don jawo hankali ga kansu, wani nau'i na zane da CNN's Jim Acosta ta cika.
Sun wuce dangantakar kafofin watsa labaru da gwamnati na yau da kullum, suna maimaita junansu wajen yin tambayoyin gotcha da nufin yin koyi da Shugaba Donald Trump kawai.
A wasu lokuta, suna sa kansu labarai, kamar lokacin da mai ba da labari na CBS Weijia Jiang ya mayar da martani ga wani "ask China" mai ba da umarni daga Trump ta hanyar yin ba-sa-baki ga wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me ya sa kake cewa da ni musamman?"
A 6 ga watan Yuli, wani taron manema labarai ya ba da misali mafi girma na rashin haɗin kan kan yadda aka daina ba da bayanan don Amurkawa.
Trump ya fada a wannan safiyar cewa, ratings na NASCAR ta talabijin ya yi rauni ne ta hanyar karyata wani laifi na ƙiyayya a kan direba Bubba Wallace da kuma shawarar da ta yanke na hana nuna tutar Confederate a abubuwan da suka faru.
A bayyane yake, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet ɗin a matsayin mai ba da rahoto bayan da mai ba da rahoto ya yi wa McEnany tambayoyin da aka tsara don ya prompt ta cewa Trump na goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany bai samar da amsar da manema labarai suke so ba - wani sautin da zai cutar da Trump - amma ta amsa akai-akai ta hanyar cewa shugaban ba ya daukar wani matsayi a kan tutar Confederate kuma cewa gist na saƙon shi ne cewa an yi wa magoya bayan NASCAR ba daidai ba ana nuna su a matsayin nuna wariyar launin fata.
