COSTA MESA, Calif. (AP) - The Los Angeles Chargers sun rattaba hannu a kan hudu daga cikin daftarinsu, ciki har da dan wasa Justin Herbert, kuma sun amince da sharuddan da sauran biyu mambobin daftarinsu aji.
The Chargers suna iya samun kwangila yi tare da daftarin aji a ranar Asabar lokacin da suka ruwaito zuwa sansanin horo don jiki da kayan aiki.
Tare da Herbert, wanda aka zaba tare da na shida overall pick, tawagar sanar da sanya hannu na wide receivers Joe Reed (fifth round) da KJ Hill (seventh round) tare da shida-round aminci Alohi Gilman.
Sun amince da sharuddan da mai tsaron baya Kenneth Murray Jr. da kuma mai tsaron baya Joshua Kelley, wanda aka zaba a zagaye na hudu.
Herbert ya fara wasanni 42 a Oregon, ya buga tarihi 29-13 tare da murza leda 10,541 da kuma 108 total touchdowns.
Ya jagoranci Ducks zuwa gasar Pac-12 a kakar da ta wuce, ya jefa touchdowns 32 da kuma shida interceptions a wasanni 14.
Ya caccaki sana'arsa da nasara a kan Wisconsin a Rose Bowl, inda ya gudu don touchdowns uku kuma aka sanya sunan m MVP.
Herbert zai yi takara da tsohon soja Tyrod Taylor don fara aiki.
The Chargers za su sami sabon dan wasan bayan Philip Rivers tashi via free agency bayan 14 seasons a matsayin mai farawa.
Murray shi ne dan wasa na 23 bayan Los Angeles ya yi ciniki da New England don ya koma zagayen farko.
